# Next.js & React Conventions

## App Router

- Dùng App Router (thư mục `app/[locale]/`)
- i18n qua `next-intl` với `[locale]` segment
- Server Components mặc định, Client Components khi cần interactivity

## Auth

### Auth.js config
```typescript
// src/lib/auth.ts — Zitadel OIDC provider
NextAuth({
  providers: [Zitadel({ clientId, issuer })],
  session: { strategy: "jwt" },
  callbacks: { jwt, session, redirect },
});
```

### API Routes
- `src/app/api/auth/[...nextauth]/route.ts` — Auth.js handler
- `src/app/api/auth/login/route.ts` — Custom login (Zitadel Session API)
- `src/app/api/auth/register/route.ts` — Custom register
- `src/app/api/auth/forgot-password/route.ts` — Forgot password
- `src/app/api/auth/reset-password/route.ts` — Reset password
- `src/app/api/auth/social/route.ts` — Social login config

### Typed API Contracts
- Define contracts in `src/lib/api-contracts.ts` (APILogin, APIRegister, etc.)
- Wrapper pattern: `src/lib/api-handler.ts` — `defaultHandler<T>()` auto-parses, validates, and error-handles
- Each route uses `defaultHandler` with typed contract for type safety

### Custom Login UI Flow
1. Form submit tới `/api/auth/login` → `defaultHandler<APILogin>()` validates + gọi Zitadel Session API
2. On success → redirect tới Zitadel OIDC authorize
3. Auth.js handle callback → `/api/auth/callback/zitadel`
4. JWT session cookie được set

### Server Actions
- `src/actions/auth.ts` — `logoutAction()` redirect tới Auth.js signout + Zitadel end_session

## Components

- **Shadcn UI** components trong `components/ui/`
- Feature components trong `components/<feature>/`
- Composition over inheritance

## State Management

- **Zustand** cho global state
- React Context chỉ cho theme/locale
- Server State: React Server Components + fetch trực tiếp

## API Calls

- Client → `credentials: "include"` (gửi cookie session)
- Server → `backendFetch()` với `Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>` từ Auth.js session
- API base URL: `process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` (https://api.puchi.io.vn)
- Middleware file: `src/lib/proxy.ts` — proxy utility cho API requests

## i18n

- Dùng `next-intl` với `useTranslations()`
- File messages trong `messages/`
- Không hardcode text trong component
